    {
      "id": "el_25",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 844,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 274,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Innermost (): (5-3)=2\n  = 2[3+{4-2}×2]\nStep 2: {}: {4-2}=2\n  = 2[3+2×2] = 2[3+4] = 14\n\nTRICK:\nAlways inside-out: ()→{}→[]\nSolve innermost bracket first\nThen apply BODMAS within each level\n\n  2[ 3 + { 4 - (5-3) } × 2 ]\n               ─────\n  2[ 3 + {  4 - 2  } × 2 ]\n          ─────────\n  2[ 3 +     2     × 2 ]\n  2[ 3 +       4        ] = 2×7 = 14\n\nAnswer: 14 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 2500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 25,
      "isDeleted": false,
