      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Innermost (): (5-3)=2\n  = 2[3+{4-2}×2]\nStep 2: {}: {4-2}=2\n  = 2[3+2×2] = 2[3+4] = 14\n\nTRICK:\nAlways inside-out: ()→{}→[]\nSolve innermost bracket first\nThen apply BODMAS within each level\n\n  2[ 3 + { 4 - (5-3) } × 2 ]\n               ─────\n  2[ 3 + {  4 - 2  } × 2 ]\n          ─────────\n  2[ 3 +     2     × 2 ]\n  2[ 3 +       4        ] = 2×7 = 14\n\nAnswer: 14 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
