    {
      "id": "el_30",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 844,
      "width": 231,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 47 = 50-3\n  (50-3)² = 2500-300+9\nStep 2: = 2209\n\nTRICK:\n(a-b)² = a²-2ab+b²\n47² = 50²-2(50)(3)+3² = 2209\n53² = 50²+300+9 = 2809\nPick nearest round number!\n\n  47² = (50-3)²\n      = 50² - 2×50×3 + 3²\n      = 2500 - 300   + 9  = 2209\n\nAnswer: 2209 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
