      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1268,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: a²-b² = (a+b)(a-b)\nStep 2: = (78+22)(78-22)\n  = 100×56 = 5600\n\nTRICK:\na²-b² = (a+b)(a-b)\nLook for sum/diff that are round numbers!\n78+22=100, 78-22=56 → easy!\n\n  78²-22² = (78+22) × (78-22)\n          =  100    ×   56\n          = 5600\n\nAnswer: 5600 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
