      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 21 = 20+1\n  (20+1)³ = 8000+1200+60+1\nStep 2: = 9261\n\nTRICK:\n(a+b)³ = a³+3a²b+3ab²+b³\nOR: a³+b³+3ab(a+b)\n= 8000+1+3(20)(1)(21) = 8001+1260\n= 9261\n\n  21³ = 20³ + 3×20²×1 + 3×20×1² + 1³\n      = 8000 +  1200   +   60    +  1\n      = 9261\n\nAnswer: 9261 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
