      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1268,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Round: 5×6+3×3\nStep 2: = 30+9 = 39\n  Exact = 39.06 (very close!)\n\nTRICK:\nRound to nearest integer\n999×45 = (1000-1)×45 = 44955\nUse (a±small) for quick estimates\n\n  4.98×6.03 + 2.97×3.04\n  ~ 5×6     + 3×3\n  =  30     +  9  = 39 (exact: 39.06)\n\nAnswer: ~39 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
