      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 37.5% = 3/8\nStep 2: 3/8 × 480 = 3×60 = 180\n\nTRICK:\nMemorize % to fraction:\n12.5%=1/8, 25%=1/4, 33.3%=1/3\n37.5%=3/8, 62.5%=5/8, 75%=3/4\nTIP: x% of y = y% of x\n\n  |████ 37.5% ████|░░░ 62.5% ░░░|\n  37.5% = 3/8\n  3/8 × 480 = 180\n\nAnswer: 180 ✓",
